snippet.title: AH3AD Trailer - Now on Windows & Android
snippet.description:
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.LinkSevenGames.AH3AD
Windows: https://linkseven.itch.io/ah3ad


Runner and puzzle merge together to form a new concept: AH3AD.
Dive into a world inspired by retro aesthetics, and feel the synth vibes as you brave through your journey.


Follow my social media to see updates and cool stuff:

Twitter: https://twitter.com/linksevengames
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/linksevengames
Facebook: https://web.facebook.com/linksevengames
